The '''Rábaköz Wind Farm''' is an under construction wind power project in [[Győr-Moson-Sopron County]], [[Hungary]]. It will have 48 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://ebrdrenewables.com/sites/renew/Lists/EBRD%20Master%20Spreadsheet/DispForm.aspx?ID=310&Source=http%3A%2F%2Febrdrenewables%2Ecom%2Fsites%2Frenew%2Fdefault%2Easpx Wind Energy Takes Off in Hungary]</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 96 [[Megawatt|MW]] of power, enough to power over 37,978 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$285 million.

